title: S.H.I.E.L.D. Credit Card V.1
shortDesc: The first generation design of the SHIELD credit card.
thumbnailURL: ./Downloads/SHIELD Creadit Card V.1/SHIELD - Credit Card - Mockup 4.png
description:
Strategic Homeland Intervention Enforcement and Logistic Division is from the Marvel Cinematic Universe.
This is a design concept for a debit card featuring a Greyscale front with a blue pattern background featuring a custom logo.
Made from merging the S.H.I.E.L.D. strike patch and the FBI logo.
